{"tid":1441841,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"連登仔女！請你地冷靜，保持清醒理性分析","createTime":"2019-08-10T18:09:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-10T19:13:22.000Z","uid":12919,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"350db8f948e83c11473986705160fbd18b32aa56","tid":1441841,"uid":12919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T18:09:47.000Z","msg":"步入八月見到好多連登仔女不停出post發表意見<br />\n<br />\n睇得出目的係為左加快爭取成功<br />\n<br />\n但係已經出現手忙腳亂，資訊唔夠清晰、地區取捨出現重大分期<br />\n<br />\n到左夢境場地物資去唔到前線，分工開始混亂<br />\n<br />\n狗屋部署變陣對付遊行，淋病耍手段想打經濟牌<br />\n<br />\n中聯辦出動同鄉會，地區黑社會製造恐怖主義<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n現時連登係文武雙全，勇武和理合作無間<br />\n<br />\n 人力物力良知樣樣齊，千萬唔好心急，要見招拆招<br />\n<br />\n唔需要主動迎接恐怖分子，但記住被打一定要還手<br />\n<br />\n場呢夢有排發，係一場超級馬拉松<br />\n<br />\n發夢發到攰就要回家好好休息，日後再搏殺<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家加油"},{"pid":"159548fdae77c529be41431bbd14a2a591444d7d","tid":1441841,"uid":109820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T18:12:11.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n<br />\n【小心中計】如果我係敵人，我會想<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1441838\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1441838</a>"},{"pid":"365abfa20622f816e8a4dfa713c48841336323f0","tid":1441841,"uid":12919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T18:26:35.000Z","msg":"唔好灰心呀連登仔女"},{"pid":"db1ba18edaabda44b44d33d57fcbea0a7ea02da2","tid":1441841,"uid":12919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T18:28:50.000Z","msg":"記得冷靜，攰就休息"},{"pid":"5020b55e67cd66666685fef89e257d3b86d21d75","tid":1441841,"uid":12919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T18:37:19.000Z","msg":"希望你地睇到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47c2cf29552955030a249fa983c8d8238a15311c","tid":1441841,"uid":55130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T18:38:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3802dda07c84be2d51c8e2f26876fda26e59fc4b","tid":14418